      == Usage question

      Our friendly volunteer community regularly answers Drools questions on StackOverflow.

    .text-center(style="margin-bottom: 10px")<
      %a.btn.btn-lg.btn-success.versionedButton(href="https://stackoverflow.com/questions/tagged/drools")<
        %img(src="question.png" alt="Question")
        %div
          %span Ask/view questions on StackOverflow
      .small
        Opinionated questions aren't welcome on StackOverflow,
        %br
        so those belong on our discussion forum below.

    :asciidoc
      To get a helpful answer, follow https://stackoverflow.com/help/how-to-ask[the StackOverflow guidelines] such as:

      * Get to the point. Keep it short.
      * Be crystal clear. Reread your question before posting it.
      * Add relevant technical details: stacktrace, code snippet, ...

